The lozenge macro can not display an exclamation mark ( ! ) in the lozenge title correctly.    The following code shows the issue:

{lozenge:title=Yahoo!7 |link=http://yahoo.com.au |color=silver|arrow=none}
{lozenge}


The title should display Yahoo!7 in plain text, but instead a page link to Yahoo!7 is displayed.   Note that using title text Yahoo\!7 has the same problem, but Yahoo!!7 behaves correctly.

